        <abstract>
            <p>Assures EK he will lose no time in writing his essay [on Erasmus Darwin].</p> 
<p>A book by Samuel Butler on Erasmus Darwin and Lamarck has been announced [<hi rend="italic">Evolution, old and new</hi> (1879)]. Will have a copy sent to EK.</p> 
